  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0002",
      "text": " 166",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0003",
      "text": "6.6.5.5  Initiator control",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        205.41,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0004",
      "text": "6.6.5.5.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        198.76,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0005",
      "text": "The Initiator Control Flags shall specify which protocols, policies or functions the Sequence Initiator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.93,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0006",
      "text": "function in the Nx_Port supplying the Service Parameters requests of the recipient or is capable of as",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.06,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0007",
      "text": "a Sequence initiator.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        187.1,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0008",
      "text": "6.6.5.5.2  Initial Process_Associator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        265.39,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0009",
      "text": "The definition of the Initial Process_Associator bits (word 0, bits 13-12) is shown in table 166.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        507.04,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0010",
      "text": "Initial Process_Associator required indicates that the Nx_Port supplying this parameter requires an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        539.88,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0011",
      "text": "Association_Header at certain Sequence boundaries (see FC-FS-2) that contains a specific initial",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        539.95,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0012",
      "text": "value in the Process_Associator field.  An Nx_Port that supports Initial Process_Associator shall sup-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        540.01,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0013",
      "text": "ply an Association_Header with an initial Responder Process_Associator value at certain Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        539.98,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0014",
      "text": "boundaries, such as when it originates an Exchange.  If an Initial Process_Associator is required or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        539.97,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0015",
      "text": "supported, then X_ID interlock also is required in Class 1 and 2.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        378.19,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0016",
      "text": "If the Responder Nx_Port to the PLOGI request requires an Initial Process_Associator and the Origi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        540.11,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0017",
      "text": "nator of the PLOGI request does not support an Initial Process_Associator, the Responder shall",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.98,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0018",
      "text": "transmit an LS_RJT indicating the Initiator Control bits are in conflict.  If the Responder Nx_Port to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.91,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0019",
      "text": "the PLOGI request does not support an Initial Process_Associator and the Originator of the PLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        539.96,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0020",
      "text": "request has indicated that Initial Process_Associator is required, the Responder shall transmit an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        539.92,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0021",
      "text": "LS_RJT indicating the Initiator Control bits are in conflict.  In either of these cases, the Nx_Ports are",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.02,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0022",
      "text": "unable to communicate.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        202.07,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0023",
      "text": "These bits only have meaning for PLOGI and PLOGI LS_ACC.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        373.77,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0024",
      "text": "6.6.5.5.3  ACK_0 capability",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        221.98,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0025",
      "text": "0 = ACK_0 incapable",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        190.15,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0026",
      "text": "1 = ACK_0 capable",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        182.33,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0027",
      "text": "The ACK_0 capability bit (word 0, bit 11) specifies if the Nx_Port supplying these Class Service Pa-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        540.01,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0028",
      "text": "rameters is capable of support for ACK_0 as a Sequence Initiator for acknowledgement of an entire",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.95,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0029",
      "text": "Sequence in either Discard or Process Exchange Error Policies.  As a Sequence Initiator an Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        540.01,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0030",
      "text": "receives and processes ACK frames in response to Data frame transmission.  ACK_0 support is ap-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.03,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0031",
      "text": "plicable to acknowledged class of service Sequences (see FC-FC-2).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        401.47,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0032",
      "text": " Table 166 – Initial Process_Associator Bits Definition",
      "bbox": [
        190.5,
        200.98,
        445.6,
        212.09
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0033",
      "text": "Word 0, bits 13-12",
      "bbox": [
        131.22,
        223.0,
        216.76,
        234.11
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0034",
      "text": "Meaning",
      "bbox": [
        357.74,
        223.0,
        398.26,
        234.11
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0035",
      "text": "00b",
      "bbox": [
        115.98,
        244.96,
        132.6,
        256.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0036",
      "text": "Initial Process_Associator not supported",
      "bbox": [
        235.96,
        244.96,
        414.37,
        256.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p185_s0037",
      "text": "01b",
      "bbox": [
        115.98,
